手美食：咖哩牛腩飯、栗米肉粒飯(其化頹飯均合)大量白米飯、奶茶、伴碟菜<br />\n<br />\n二手解讀：咖哩牛飯可算是肉眼觀察中常見的二手飯，皆因薯仔太濟，牛腩太有咬口，雖然不少快餐店﹙如大快活﹚，其咖哩牛腩飯味道不錯，但七成以上人仍會食唔曬。至於被視為頹飯的栗米肉粒，往往是不少人揀無可揀之選，進食意慾不高，自然吃剩機會也大。另伴碟菜更是二手飯食客必食之選---伴碟菜由於只為點綴或「叫做有條菜」，通常白烚了事，因味同嚼蠟，所以食客通常棄之一旁。其實食菜有益，二手食客實不容錯過。<br />\n<br />\n建議在進店前，先看水牌，如見有咖哩牛腩和栗米肉粒，能飽餐一頓二手飯的機會勁大。"},{"pid":"78ec4f20a61d2b1fcf65133126199a75befd7227","tid":2486863,"uid":255474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874e38399f4bea8f7910de635335cc6f97b3cd77","tid":2486863,"uid":186232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以比啖飯我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"剩返幾多錢"},{"pid":"db11ad1729c6dbcedff37768c53706b861711a34","tid":2486863,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"何不食肉糜"},{"pid":"ea65fb8308e5e348eba1b346f136d82b906f1171","tid":2486863,"uid":186232,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"47cb39262a62be465b0d203d6fbbf8d1fa218e61","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c79c4bd924c37d6aed68b9e9f92ceef4743bcf","tid":2486863,"uid":287107,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9e0ccc8c323d0803ee61f19eb6bf7721a2fe2bad","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"西九8樓啦<br />\n踎一個下午 飽到你嘔<br />\n唔洗我教啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/blah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"2手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IkfemqLggy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIkfemqLggy0&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2B