40:08.000Z","msg":"同屋企人住定自己住<br />\n痴餐啦<br />\n拎綜援先啦"},{"pid":"10ce5f14bf3d76561747a33b253941e221b47244","tid":2486863,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fd32008fa88b3eff5493efe787f0392d53b3ba5","tid":2486863,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4293cfc1e59c5d7755f7ab3c4bd02b5d94568f13","tid":2486863,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3e464c339eb7e29ec5e74df20046873580ea79f","tid":2486863,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:37:05.000Z","msg":"咁早有得派？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:38:09.000Z","msg":"油麻地<br />\n砵蘭街<br />\n露宿者之家<br />\n12:30pm<br />\n5:30pm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:39:24.000Z","msg":"我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話今日<br />\n我有朋友都住過露宿者之家<br />\n不過好似話就拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:41:45.000Z","msg":"露宿者行動委員會（油麻地砵蘭街69號二樓)"},{"pid":"ed77236f38fff6b33eeae4d001e1feddceb8efdc","tid":2486863,"uid":331739,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c09909c9745d094fcc152b2768cebeb67a6d1797","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"我們的互聯網，在助人尋美食的openrice，卻沒有教人搵二手飯的指南。事實上，香港雖然餐廳處處，但不是哪裡也有合適的二手飯，所以要做流浪者，就必須要對鄰近食肆有充掌握。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳1：麥當勞<br />\n<br />\n常見二手美食：薯條、薯餅、可樂、熱香餅、熱香餅專用蜜糖<br />\n<br />\n二手解讀：每位食客離開後，餐盤上幾乎例必留下前三款食物，如閣下是嗜炸物，保證能大快朵頣。熱香餅因有三塊之多，部分女食客可能會食剩一塊半塊，好運者甚至可發現少量豬柳漢堡！另要留意熱香餅用蜜糖，常有餅剩。踏入秋季唇乾舌燥，可充當真蜜糖沖水飲作滋潤喉嚨之用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餐廳2：連鎖快餐廳(美心大家樂大快活均可)<br />\n<br />\n常見二手美食：咖哩牛腩飯、栗米肉粒飯(其化頹飯均合)大量白米飯、奶茶、伴碟菜<br />\n<br />\n二手解讀：咖哩牛飯可算是肉眼觀察中常見的二手飯，皆因薯仔太濟，牛腩太有咬口，雖然不少快餐店﹙如大快活﹚，其咖哩牛腩飯味道不錯，但七成以上人仍會食唔曬。至於被視為頹飯的栗米肉粒，往往是不少人揀無可揀之選，進食意慾不高，自然吃剩機會也大。另伴碟菜更是二手飯食客必食之選---伴碟菜由於只為點綴或「叫做有條菜」，通常白烚了事，因味同嚼蠟，所以食客通常棄之一旁。其實食菜有益，二手食客實不容錯過。<br />\n<br />\n建議在進店前，先看水牌，如見有咖哩牛腩和栗米肉粒，能飽餐一頓二手飯的機會勁大。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:42:08.000Z","msg":"地點呢？<br />\n邊度多港女食？ 唔想食廢老二手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e349681c9afc377d55cc95ec8f7877b92eae374","tid":2486863,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36182c10e28f258cf10c3584be3242ceee406ad1","tid":2486863,"uid":186232,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"6499092589a7adf7df627933e741a091076aab31","tid":2486863,"uid":9253,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"擺低Payme link,我比$50 你食飯"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打好心 我唔要錢但想要一份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:46:58.000Z","msg":"咁你就唔好話咩就快餓死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6858642ec5fbd8d00e78501c61cb298864ea08","tid":2486863,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47cb39262a62be465b0d203d6fbbf8d1fa218e61","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c79c4bd924c37d6aed68b9e9f92ceef4743bcf","tid":2486863,"uid":287107,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9e0ccc8c323d0803ee61f19eb6bf7721a2fe2bad","tid":2486863,"uid":242537,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"西九8樓啦<br />\n踎一個下午 飽到你嘔<br />\n唔洗我教啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/blah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"2手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IkfemqLggy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIkfemqLggy0&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=569ba0db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ikfem